Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:18.29,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a big gun, I took it from my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:21.74,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,Sick with Justice, I just wanna feel you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.97,0:00:25.15,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your angel, only a ring away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:28.50,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,You make me violate you, no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:38.62,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all up to you, no one lives forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:42.21,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,Been burn in the hell, by all those pigs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:45.48,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been hell, from when I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:48.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,They make me violate them, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:52.21,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down on your knees!\NGet a good head on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:55.64,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's for your guys, go to the end of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:58.95,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you think, give it with dedication...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:02.22,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put out your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:05.62,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,You made a mess! For Christ sakes, this rotten world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:09.05,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit out of luck! Go with my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:12.49,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,Light up the fire! Right on the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.49,0:01:15.85,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:24.43,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapon... I have it all!

Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这眼神算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.02,0:01:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被蹂躏得这么惨还没学乖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么鄙视我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 把那个耍刀的解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没人来买你…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就把你送到 从早到晚都磕药磕个完的变态那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种家伙不来点激烈的SM满足不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你被他用药调教了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天摇着屁股连大便都吃的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你思维也会有所改善的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你的录像出来了 我也会买上一盘的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴 赌输了就乱发彪吗 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你带“芝宝”了吗 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:29.91,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（芝宝：Zippo 打火机）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来你听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙结果还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很吵啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真弄不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我亲爱的莱薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well,my dear Revy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到这里来干吧呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和我上床吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you did wanna fuck,huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿银 阿银
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢在太岁头上动土
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想见识我的刀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就全员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手拉着手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下极乐净土去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀光他们 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them all BABY！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 看呐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种乱战我还没从见过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别躲起来让他们见识下男人气概
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑起来跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's all yours
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下不动真格的不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雪绪这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点跟来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼 疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 那女人好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到能在这得到和她对干的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准备准备舞台怎行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁放的什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗发精？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:04:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strike
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我投降 我投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give GiveGiveGive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.52,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Give：Give Up 投降）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给？ 给我什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give? Give me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can not speak…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想给我什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your gonna give me something right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well come on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你他妈到底想说些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the fuck are trying so say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 我说我Give了啦 真的 Give GiveGiveGive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵了 你这蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quit yapping you goofball
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底给还是不给 来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna give it to me or not? Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 大块头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Jumbo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The gams's up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在情况一团糟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boy we made a mess
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只好彻底扫荡一遍这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we got left is to mop-up the place
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们分头行动 把那头猪和公主搜出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后沿着走廊在泳池会合 OK？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到我家洛克的话也一起带过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他干得好的话 说不定和公主一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:05:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么交给你了哦 搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以理解的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽中下下签了啊 真是可怜你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也别想活着从这出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是地狱旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:19.24,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（地狱旅馆：美国恐怖电影Motel Hell中的地狱旅馆）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被黑人吃掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.50,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（黑人：指剧中杀人鬼 Michael.Melvin）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是打野鸭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永生去吧 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time to live forever Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音 听不到声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火枪 难道其他人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 火枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听见了啦 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？恐怕都死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么口气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经受够跟你混了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空说废话 就去找那女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我怎么办啊 计划都支离破碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 想开溜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是令人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你会杀手下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,评价越来越低了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你还这么生龙活虎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是还没遇到那大块头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女枪手还是第一次见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于有机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我睡一晚吧 小莱薇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为的就是这个？ 笑死人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:08:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这罐子落地那刻就是开始信号哦 小猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 十 九 八 七
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为自己是西部枪手跟我对决吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁有时间陪你这连三流都不如的贱货 蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很想杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你要是恨不得不被我杀就要另当别论了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定由大块头处理你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婊子 你妈地站住 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 贱货
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 我叫你站住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉让你久等了 大块头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting,jumbo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你想见的家伙带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you,your prom date
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真他妈没趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你苍蝇啊 耍刀的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐早就不在了 被我杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了？ 那就快给我滚回去烤你的章鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你这种有点小聪明的小狗仔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能偷到钱袋里的钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子…有种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 让我见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拨枪的时机由你选吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个 这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了你 我杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静下来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱薇和银次先生似乎干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一 再等一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈岛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要来这？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从知道你被“我们的工作”卷了进来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一无所知呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说我被“卷了进来”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说错了 冈岛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是站在那中心的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪绪 你说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈岛先生 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承了鹫峰组第十四代总代的位子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便是鹫峰组实质上的最高权力者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 不是被卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是原本就站在那中心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你 是我的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是明知“这边”是什么样的地方还踏进来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到了吧 充满恶意不懂分辨事物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种人在背叛 厮杀着 就是这样的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈岛先生 我再问一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是为何而来？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我刚才说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能看着你被卷进来而置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置之不理？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为板东的死是自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当然也在场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织失去推进力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与顶上的组织疏远
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须与强大的势力对抗之时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能救其出苦境的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你一个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结拜弟兄的复权
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不承认亲属以外之人的继承
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则就是这样定的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么想 这都是故意找碴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管这是多么无理的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也只剩这一条路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们黑道的法则
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的人生又怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不希望这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,板东 阿银 连你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家为了使你远离争斗而拼尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让你不站在“这”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 我能来“这”更早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 该恨的是香砂会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 只是强迫自己一个人背负责任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到的只有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得在咖啡屋谈的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人 与筛子是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个法国人说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人啊 要把自己扔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往自己决定的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是被逼 而是自己选择了它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为父亲 为追随父亲的人尽我所能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是不得不选择
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你看这步看错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就必须把多余的东西也一同背负
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你站在黄昏下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你一直停留在黄昏下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能往“这”来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“自己选的”不这样想怎能作出觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人的生命 名誉 未来都关系在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我除了为这些战斗还有什么选择
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是自己想“自己选的” 就不可能撑得下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 相信那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只到由于莫须有的罪名 被巡警打个半死的那晚上为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 如果你再提回正常位的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就不再是同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与那个时候 没有分别
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这孩子经历的这晚经验面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对这个在自己眼前滚落到你们那边的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无言以对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 就在我站在的这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.85,0:17:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在除此之外的任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脚 根本没站在任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个…鬼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然觉得给你的死法是有点便宜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过程度正好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了 发生的事情全部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好事 坏事都由我来背负
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样大家与阿银都能得救的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪绪 你对阿银…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈岛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么站在这？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在咖啡屋时说的话 其实我当时并不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可现在我想我能明明白白跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是为什么逃入东南亚的黑社会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许你还想追求日本 不 想追求日常生活中的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最后你其实什么都没有选择
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有回到平稳的每日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有踏进充满罪恶的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 在这止步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾经说过 你想救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那请救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救鹫峰组 救阿银 救所有的组员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能做得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你 并非想救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是不想失去本被丢掉的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果对我见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你对日本留下的追忆就会连最后的碎片都不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都没背负
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连对本被自己丢掉的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都还抱着一丝憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的你 到底能保护谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的你 到底能拯救谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 来 回答我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想普通活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与不想痛苦活下去的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本应该站在同样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪绪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在不甘心忍受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我 讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:19:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干了件很有趣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子弹哦 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把子弹斩成了两半
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能再让我看一次啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能心急
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和翻译对我有恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必白白浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运气好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 运气差的话 总会有干架的机会的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪绪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次真是万分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我 希望今后永不要相见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克还没回房间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 在哪儿磨蹭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正这段时间没他们出场的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对鹫峰组的奇袭 将在07:50开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本部事务所除外 其他所有确认了情况的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派两个分队过去给予歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击部队 已经出发了
